Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.15,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}乘上小船靜靜漂蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.49,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}雙臂緊抱膝蓋
